('96602','33336','5','This newly built villa is currently built on a 1.900m² large 1st sea line plot. The luxury villa offers 900m² of living space on about a light-filled living-dining room, modern fitted kitchen with quality brand built-in appliances, utility room and storage rooms, 4 bedrooms with 4 bathrooms en suite, dressing room in the master bedroom and sep. Guest apartment. The two residential floors are connected to the garage with a lift. The underground car park (6 pitches) can be reached by car via a Carlift. You can relax on the chic outdoor pool with sun terrace and barbecue area. High-quality technology, air conditioning and underfloor heating complete the offerings.'),
